Physiotherapist
30 Apr 2014 09:44 PM - UAE
A fantastic opportunity currently exists for a number of physiotherapists to work for a well renowned hospital based in Abu Dhabi. The multi speciality hospital strives to provide the highest level of specialised patient care, from the first diagnosis to the management and treatment of all cases.This medical centre is a new state-of-the-art fully equipped modern healthcare facility. Their primary focus is to offer first class healthcare.The hospital is currently looking for physiotherapists with experience in the following areas:• Paediatrics• Cardiovascular• Rehabilitation• General PhysiotherapyCandidates who wish to apply must possess the following:• Bachelors degree• Experience within the one of the above disciplines• Minimum 2 years experience• HAAD license is advantageous but not essentialApply
